name: GettysburgCollegePhoneDirectory
0:
”Alexa, open Gettysburg College Phone Directory”
”Alexa, find John Doe with Gettysburg College Phone Directory”
”read next results”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gettysburg college phone directory
des:
To find an employee's extension, say "find" and then the employee's name. You can search by first name or first name and last name automatically by saying the name, or you can specify a last name search by including the words "last name" in your search. If there happen to be multiple results from your search, you can say next, repeat, and previous, to navigate the results and find the desired employee's extension. 
Additionally, if Alexa is having trouble spelling your voice input, you can spell by letter as well. If you want to spell both first name and last name, spell by letter and say "space" to divide the two words. This app makes it easy to find extensions for employees in Gettysburg College.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
